==Translingual==
===Etymology===
From the northern constellation '''[[Cassiopeia]]''', because of its proximity to the [[celestial pole]].
===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''''Cassiope'''''
#{{botany}}: A [[taxonomic]] [[genus]] of [[circumboreal]] [[shrub]]s in the family [[Ericaceae]].  The plants are used as [[fuel]] by native peoples in the [[Arctic]]..